  missionTitle: Badlav Ke Paanch Saal
  completionTitle: CHAPTER 17 COMPLETE
  completionMessage: Five-year public audit pass hua. Pradesh model ko doosre fictional
    regions ne study karna shuru kiya.
  chapterNumber: 17
  nextChapterScene: 
  introTitle: CHAPTER 17 / BADLAV KE PAANCH SAAL
  introMessage: Announcement ek din ka hota hai. Health, learning, safety aur rozgaar
    ka badlav paanch saal maangta hai.
  objectives:
  - {fileID: 473753320}
  - {fileID: 1967487015}
  - {fileID: 725496076}
  - {fileID: 1518961061}
  - {fileID: 1892702538}
  - {fileID: 1025420081}
  - {fileID: 885434134}
  - {fileID: 1504445392}
  - {fileID: 1261111765}
  - {fileID: 1636263500}
  - {fileID: 2120191509}
  - {fileID: 740891478}
  objectiveLabels:
  - Independent baseline, sample limits and correction history verify karein
  - Clinic access, medicine availability and referral outcomes deliver karein
  - High-risk maternal referral, newborn follow-up and nutrition network run karein
  - Reading, maths, attendance and teacher-support outcomes scale karein
  - Skills, enterprise survival, fair credit and producer-market outcomes deliver
    karein
  - Samrat ke saath response, evidence, survivor support and appeal outcomes review
    karein
  - Measured phased reforms ya simultaneous mega announcements mein decision lein
  - Rural water, referral, school transport, maintenance and producer outcomes deliver
    karein
  - Transport, waste, air, safe-street, clinic and vendor-zone outcomes deliver karein
  - Complaints, recusals, recoveries, whistleblower safety and appeals audit karein
  - Targets, misses, costs and corrections ka equal-question public report defend
    karein
  - Independent panel par four outcomes and full-term public audit dekhein
  milestoneSteps: 03000000070000000a000000
  milestoneTitles:
  - HEALTH BASELINE MOVING
  - BALANCED REFORM ACTIVE
  - RURAL-URBAN AUDIT READY
  milestoneMessages:
  - Baseline, primary health and maternal-child systems measured hain. Learning and
    livelihood next hain.
  - Learning, livelihood, safety and reform strategy active hain. Rural-urban execution
    next hai.
  - Rural, urban and integrity outcomes audited. Five-year public report final review
    unlock karega.
